<h3 id="shopify-award">Shopify Award</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Choose a Shopify Award recipient with full-time faculty</li>
  <li>Someone who upholds the Shopify value system – “getting shit done”</li>
  <li>Someone who <em>may</em> work at Shopify – not a requirement</li>
  <li>$1000 cheque to the student</li>
  <li>We’ll present it in a gathering of all third year students at the start of the year
    <ul>
      <li>List of 3rd year students</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>My pick:
    <ul>
      <li>Kelly Miles</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

